  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large pot over medium heat and saute the onion and garlic until softened",
    "Add the crab meat and cook until heated through",
    "Add the fish sauce, lime juice, and bay leaves, and stir to combine",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 5 minutes",
    "Cook the rice noodles according to package instructions and drain",
    "Stir-fry the tomato in a little oil until softened",
    "To assemble the dish, place some noodles in a bowl, add the crab mixture, and top with stir-fried tomato",
    "Season with salt to taste",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy"
